{"tid":2268913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集 721 編導被捕","createTime":"2020-11-03T06:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T08:43:44.000Z","uid":262592,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24920807a12bf1dc8b6fe440b45a43c4e56dfd44","tid":2268913,"uid":262592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"消息指，香港電台一名負責《鏗鏘集》7.21 專題的記者，今日被警察上門拘捕，據了解涉及 7.21 相關報道，涉事的是港台節目製作人員工會前主席蔡玉玲。 <br />\n<br />\n港台《鏗鏘集》分別在去年 7 月底和今年 7 月中，播出兩集和元朗 7.21 襲擊有關的專題《元朗黑夜》和《誰主真相》，整理了大量事發當日的閉路電視片段，顯示警方在當日下午已多次在白衣人聚集的地方巡視，《誰主真相》更揭發有懷疑手持委任證的便衣警員，當晚早在鳳攸北街徘徊，目睹大批白衣人手持武器聚集卻沒有任何行動，兩集節目蔡玉玲都有參與。<br />\n<br />\n《立場》向港台工會查詢，港台工會指正了解事件，會提供協助，警方則尚待回覆。"},{"pid":"ab7afc84ee735f87c53611496752bd8cb4003795","tid":2268913,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4d5cc660d3453a86c6c9f800e6f2e9c0a510f8","tid":2268913,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"必推"},{"pid":"6017e5c33f8c8d94a633c636d824b62bff4151c3","tid":2268913,"uid":370663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"又9拉人"},{"pid":"7a9b2e66dd74114be052120f8a8a7625ff3adceb","tid":2268913,"uid":41288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:54:24.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖"},{"pid":"18a95ae1be2c9db0117be59d2970d561de081f23","tid":2268913,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a136a01ed132cb69ea5e90ae212e9be50464354","tid":2268913,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T